{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T00:38:02.185Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Grounding and quote extraction"},{"type":"text","text":" forces the model to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"locate evidence first"},{"type":"text","text":" before answering, dramatically reducing hallucination and making verification easy in long-context tasks."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The key technique:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"For long documents, ask the model to quote relevant passages before answering. This forces it to locate evidence first, rather than generating from a vague impression of the content.\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Grounding Is"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Definition"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Grounding is a prompt engineering technique used in LLMs where the user provides specific and relevant context within the prompt.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Purpose:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Infuses LLM prompts with your internal data — including structured data (Excel spreadsheets, CRM data) and unstructured data (PDFs, chat logs, email messages, blog posts) — 'grounding' the prompt in relevant context.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simplest method:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Copying and pasting relevant data directly into the prompt's context window.\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Quote Extraction Matters"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Dramatically Reduces Hallucination"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Grounding dramatically reduces hallucination. If the model can't find a relevant quote, that's a useful signal — the answer might not be in the document.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evidence-first"},{"type":"text","text":" — Model must find quotes before answering\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification easy"},{"type":"text","text":" — See quotes + answer side-by-side\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Signal of missing info"},{"type":"text","text":" — If no quote found, answer might not exist"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Forces Evidence Location"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"This forces it to locate evidence first, rather than generating from a vague impression of the content.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Without grounding:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Model generates from vague impression\n- Risk of hallucination\n- Hard to verify"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"With grounding:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Model locates exact quotes\n- Evidence-based answer\n- Easy to verify"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Enables Verification"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Ask for quotes first — grounding reduces hallucination and makes verification easy.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Check quote"},{"type":"text","text":" — Is it from the document?\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Check answer"},{"type":"text","text":" — Does it match the quote?\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Check completeness"},{"type":"text","text":" — Are all relevant quotes included?"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Quote Extraction Patterns"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern 1: Query-First, Quote-Second"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"First, extract the exact quotes from the contract that relate to termination clauses. Place them in "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"<quotes>"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":" tags. Then, based only on those quotes, summarize the termination conditions in plain language.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<document>\n{{CONTRACT_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nFirst, extract the exact quotes from the contract that relate to\ntermination clauses. Place each quote in <quote> tags with:\n- The exact text\n- The section number\n- The page number (if available)\n\n<quotes>\n<quote>\ntext: \"The agreement may be terminated by either party...\"\nsection: \"Section 12.3\"\npage: \"Page 45\"\n</quote>\n\n<quote>\ntext: \"Termination shall take effect 30 days after notice...\"\nsection: \"Section 12.4\"\npage: \"Page 45\"\n</quote>\n</quotes>\n\nThen, based ONLY on those quotes, summarize the termination\nconditions in plain language."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key elements:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Query first"},{"type":"text","text":" — Ask for quotes before answer\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Exact quotes"},{"type":"text","text":" — Use verbatim text\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" — Section, page number\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tags"},{"type":"text","text":" — Wrap in "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<quotes>"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Constraint"},{"type":"text","text":" — \"Based ONLY on those quotes\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern 2: Quote-Then-Answer Chain"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Quote-First Analysis — Ask Claude to quote relevant parts of the documents first before carrying out its task. Then based on that quoted text, ask specific questions in the prompt.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<document>\n{{FULL_DOCUMENT_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nSTEP 1: Extract Quotes\nFind and extract all quotes that mention \"revenue growth\".\nFor each quote:\n- Include exact text\n- Note page/section\n- Explain why it's relevant\n\nSTEP 2: Answer Questions\nBased ONLY on the quotes from Step 1:\n1. What are the revenue growth projections?\n2. How do expenses compare to last quarter?\n3. What risks are mentioned?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Two-step process"},{"type":"text","text":" — Clear separation\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Grounding"},{"type":"text","text":" — Answer based on quotes\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification"},{"type":"text","text":" — See quotes + reasoning"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern 3: Multiple Document Citation"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Label your sources — indexed, tagged documents let the model cite where each claim comes from.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<documents>\n<document index=\"1\">\n<source>Q3 Earnings Report</source>\n<content>{{EARNINGS_REPORT_TEXT}}</content>\n</document>\n\n<document index=\"2\">\n<source>Competitor Analysis</source>\n<content>{{COMPETITOR_ANALYSIS_TEXT}}</content>\n</document>\n</documents>\n\nFind all quotes about revenue growth.\nFor each quote:\n- Include exact text\n- Cite document index\n- Cite page/section\n\n<quotes>\n<quote source=\"document_1\">\ntext: \"The company projected 15% revenue growth for Q4.\"\nsource: Q3 Earnings Report, Page 12\n</quote>\n\n<quote source=\"document_2\">\ntext: \"Competitor X launched similar product.\"\nsource: Competitor Analysis, Page 8\n</quote>\n</quotes>\n\nCompare revenue growth between both documents."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Indexed documents"},{"type":"text","text":" — Each has number\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Citation required"},{"type":"text","text":" — Model cites sources\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Source attribution"},{"type":"text","text":" — \"document_1\", \"document_2\"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification"},{"type":"text","text":" — Can check each source"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern 4: Quote Matching Criteria"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"I am using GPT 4 Turbo to extract quotations from a large document. My goal is to find all quotations that match criteria specified in my prompt.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<document>\n{{FULL_DOCUMENT_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nCriteria for quotes:\n- Must mention \"customer satisfaction\"\n- Must include a metric or percentage\n- Must be from Q3 or Q4 sections\n\nFind all quotes matching these criteria:\n\n<quotes>\n<quote>\ntext: \"Our customer satisfaction score improved to 92% in Q3.\"\nsection: \"Q3 Results\"\npage: \"Page 15\"\nmatches_criteria: \"Yes - mentions customer satisfaction, includes metric, from Q3\"\n</quote>\n\n<quote>\ntext: \"We achieved 95% satisfaction in Q4, exceeding our target.\"\nsection: \"Q4 Highlights\"\npage: \"Page 22\"\nmatches_criteria: \"Yes - mentions customer satisfaction, includes metric, from Q4\"\n</quote>\n</quotes>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Specific criteria"},{"type":"text","text":" — Clear matching rules\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verification"},{"type":"text","text":" — Can check each criterion\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Score"},{"type":"text","text":" — Rate likelihood of match"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern 5: Quote Scoring for Selection"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Maybe ask the LLM to generate a score from 1 to 100 of how likely each paragraph is to match your criteria and then you make the cutoff yourself.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<document>\n{{FULL_DOCUMENT_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nFor each paragraph that mentions \"innovation\":\n1. Extract the exact quote\n2. Score how well it matches (1-100)\n3. Note why it matches\n\nFound paragraphs:\n\n<quotes>\n<quote score=\"95\">\ntext: \"Our innovation strategy focuses on AI-driven solutions.\"\nscore_reason: \"Directly mentions innovation, specific about AI focus\"\n</quote>\n\n<quote score=\"80\">\ntext: \"We are committed to innovation in all areas.\"\nscore_reason: \"Mentions innovation but vague\"\n</quote>\n\n<quote score=\"60\">\ntext: \"The company will continue to innovate.\"\nscore_reason: \"Generic mention, no specifics\"\n</quote>\n</quotes>\n\nSelect all quotes with score >= 70."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Score ranking"},{"type":"text","text":" — Prioritize best matches\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cutoff control"},{"type":"text","text":" — You decide threshold\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" — See why scored high/low"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern 6: Chunk-Based Extraction"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"So breaking into smaller chunks is good.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Chunk 1 (Pages 1-50):\n<document index=\"1\" part=\"1\">\n{{FIRST_CHUNK_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nChunk 2 (Pages 51-100):\n<document index=\"1\" part=\"2\">\n{{SECOND_CHUNK_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nChunk 3 (Pages 101-150):\n<document index=\"1\" part=\"3\">\n{{THIRD_CHUNK_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nFor each chunk, extract quotes about \"revenue\":\n\n<quotes>\n<quote chunk=\"1\">\ntext: \"Revenue increased by 15%.\"\npage: \"Page 25\"\n</quote>\n\n<quote chunk=\"2\">\ntext: \"Q3 revenue reached $5M.\"\npage: \"Page 75\"\n</quote>\n</quotes>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Handle large docs"},{"type":"text","text":" — Break into chunks\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Track origin"},{"type":"text","text":" — Know which chunk\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complete coverage"},{"type":"text","text":" — Process all chunks"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grounding Techniques"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Technique 1: Static Grounding"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Static grounding: Facts embedded directly in the prompt. Good for stable, small fact sets (brand guidelines, product specs, common policies).\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<grounding_context>\nBrand Guidelines:\n- Tone: Professional but accessible\n- No jargon without explanation\n- Include 2-3 practical examples\n\nProduct Specs:\n- Free tier: 1,000 tokens/month\n- Pro tier: 100,000 tokens/month\n- Enterprise: Custom pricing\n</grounding_context>\n\n<document>\n{{DOCUMENT_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nBased ONLY on the grounding context above, write a marketing\nemail for the Pro tier."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stable facts"},{"type":"text","text":" — Brand guidelines\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Small sets"},{"type":"text","text":" — Product specs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Policies"},{"type":"text","text":" — Common rules"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Technique 2: Dynamic Grounding (RAG)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Dynamic grounding (RAG): Facts retrieved per-query from a vector DB or search index. Good for large or frequently-changing knowledge (docs, support articles, internal wikis).\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<grounding_context>\n[Retrieved from vector DB based on query]\n\nDocument 1: \"Customer satisfaction improved to 92% in Q3.\"\nDocument 2: \"Revenue growth projections for Q4: 15%.\"\nDocument 3: \"Operating expenses increased by 8%.\"\n</grounding_context>\n\nUsing ONLY the retrieved context above, answer:\n\"What are the key Q3-Q4 metrics?\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Large knowledge"},{"type":"text","text":" — Full docs, articles\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Frequently changing"},{"type":"text","text":" — Support articles\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Internal wikis"},{"type":"text","text":" — Company knowledge"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Technique 3: Tool-Call Grounding"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Tool-call grounding: Model calls a function to fetch facts on demand (database lookup, API call). Good for exact-answer data (account balances, inventory counts).\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Available tools:\n- get_account_balance(user_id)\n- get_order_details(order_id)\n- get_stock_quote(ticker)\n\nUser query: \"What's my account balance?\"\n\nModel should:\n1. Call get_account_balance(user_id=\"12345\")\n2. Return result: \"$1,234.56\"\n3. Ground answer in exact result"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Exact answers"},{"type":"text","text":" — Account balances\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Inventory"},{"type":"text","text":" — Stock counts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Real-time"},{"type":"text","text":" — Stock prices"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Technique 4: Explicit Rule for \"Don't Know\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Add an explicit rule: 'If the answer isn't in the provided context, say you don't know. Never guess.'\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Template:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<document>\n{{DOCUMENT_TEXT}}\n</document>\n\nRULE: If the answer isn't in the provided context, say \"I don't know.\"\nNever guess or hallucinate.\n\nQuestion: What is the termination clause?\n\n<quotes>\n<quote>\ntext: \"The agreement may be terminated by either party...\"\nsection: \"Section 12.3\"\n</quote>\n</quotes>\n\nAnswer: [Based only on quote above]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prevents guessing"},{"type":"text","text":" — No hallucination\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Clear signal"},{"type":"text","text":" — \"I don't know\" when no info\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Trustworthy"},{"type":"text","text":" — Only state what's in context"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best Practices for Grounding"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Put Facts Before Task"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Put facts before the task. Model sees context first, task second.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pattern:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"xml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<context>\n[Grounding facts]\n</context>\n\n<task>\n[Instructions and query]\n</task>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Separate Clearly"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Separate clearly. Use "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"<docs>"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":", "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"<context>"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":", or markdown sections. The model is better at 'refer to the context' when context is visibly delimited.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tags to use:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<docs>"},{"type":"text","text":" — Document wrapper\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<context>"},{"type":"text","text":" — Grounding context\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<grounding_context>"},{"type":"text","text":" — Explicit grounding\n- Markdown sections ("},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"---"},{"type":"text","text":") — Visual separation"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Don't Pad"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Don't pad. Irrelevant context degrades quality (middle-forgetting effect; attention dilution). If a fact isn't useful for this query, leave it out.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Avoid:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Irrelevant context"},{"type":"text","text":" — Wastes attention\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Middle-forgetting"},{"type":"text","text":" — Model loses focus\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Attention dilution"},{"type":"text","text":" — Too much noise"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Chunk Strategically"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Chunking affects everything. Chunk size, overlap, and whether you chunk by fixed length or semantic boundary (paragraph, section) — all impact quality. Default to semantic chunks at paragraph or section level.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practice:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Semantic chunks"},{"type":"text","text":" — Paragraph or section level\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Avoid fixed length"},{"type":"text","text":" — Can break coherence\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consider overlap"},{"type":"text","text":" — Maintain context"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5. Re-rank Retrieved Content"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Re-rank. After initial retrieval, run a cross-encoder re-ranker to pick the best subset. Easy +10-20% relevance.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Initial retrieval"},{"type":"text","text":" — Get top-k results\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Re-rank"},{"type":"text","text":" — Cross-encoder scores\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Pick best"},{"type":"text","text":" — Select subset"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"6. Top-K Calibration"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Top-K is a calibration choice. Retrieve too few — miss relevant context. Retrieve too many — dilute the prompt. Start at 5.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Guideline:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Start at 5"},{"type":"text","text":" — Default Top-K\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Too few"},{"type":"text","text":" — Miss context\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Too many"},{"type":"text","text":" — Dilute prompt"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"7. Quote Exact Text"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"First, extract the exact quotes... Place them in <quotes> tags.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key requirements:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Exact text"},{"type":"text","text":" — Verbatim from document\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No paraphrasing"},{"type":"text","text":" — Use original words\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tags"},{"type":"text","text":" — Wrap in "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<quotes>"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"8. Include Metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For each quote, include:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Exact text"},{"type":"text","text":" — Verbatim\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Section number"},{"type":"text","text":" — Document section\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Page number"},{"type":"text","text":" — If available\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Source document"},{"type":"text","text":" — For multiple docs"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"9. Constrain to Quotes"},{"type":"text","text":" ⭐"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Then, based ONLY on those quotes, summarize the termination conditions in plain language.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Explicit constraint:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Based ONLY on those quotes\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prevents hallucination"},{"type":"text","text":" — No outside info\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evidence-based"},{"type":"text","text":" — Grounded in quotes\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Verifiable"},{"type":"text","text":" — Can trace to quotes"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Summary"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Grounding and quote extraction"},{"type":"text","text":" forces evidence-first answering, reducing hallucination:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What grounding is:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Definition"},{"type":"text","text":" — Provide specific context in prompt\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Purpose"},{"type":"text","text":" — Infuse with internal data\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simplest method"},{"type":"text","text":" — Copy/paste into context window"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why quote extraction matters:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reduces hallucination"},{"type":"text","text":" — Dramatically\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Forces evidence location"},{"type":"text","text":" — Locate before answering\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enables verification"},{"type":"text","text":" — See quotes + answer"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5 quote extraction patterns:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Query-first, quote-second"},{"type":"text","text":" — Extract quotes, then answer\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quote-then-answer chain"},{"type":"text","text":" — Two-step process\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multiple document citation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Indexed, tagged sources\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quote matching criteria"},{"type":"text","text":" — Specific matching rules\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quote scoring"},{"type":"text","text":" — Rate 1-100, cutoff control"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4 grounding techniques:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Static grounding"},{"type":"text","text":" — Facts in prompt\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Dynamic grounding (RAG)"},{"type":"text","text":" — Retrieved per-query\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool-call grounding"},{"type":"text","text":" — Fetch on demand\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Explicit \"don't know\" rule"},{"type":"text","text":" — Never guess"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"7 best practices:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Put facts before task"},{"type":"text","text":" — Context first\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Separate clearly"},{"type":"text","text":" — Use tags\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Don't pad"},{"type":"text","text":" — No irrelevant context\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chunk strategically"},{"type":"text","text":" — Semantic chunks\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Re-rank"},{"type":"text","text":" — +10-20% relevance\n6. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Top-K calibration"},{"type":"text","text":" — Start at 5\n7. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quote exact text"},{"type":"text","text":" — Verbatim"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Additional best practices:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Include metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" — Section, page, source\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Constrain to quotes"},{"type":"text","text":" — \"Based ONLY on quotes\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Grounding dramatically reduces hallucination. If the model can't find a relevant quote, that's a useful signal — the answer might not be in the document.\""}]}]}}
